<header class="article-header clearfix">
	<h1 class="article-title" itemprop="headline">
					<a href="/index.php/en/" itemprop="url" title="A simple interface for OpenPGP email security">
				A simple interface for OpenPGP email security</a>
			</h1>

			</header>
  
  <!-- Aside -->
    <!-- //Aside -->

  
        
  
  
	
  
	
	<section class="article-content clearfix" itemprop="articleBody">
		<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-5"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><img style="margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 20px; min-width: 360px;" src="/images/screenshots/mailview.png" alt="Enigmail automatically decrypts and verifies your Email" /></span></div>
<div class="col-md-5">
<h3>Why encrypt emails?</h3>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 130%;">Do you want to send your digital letters as post cards? Probably not.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 130%;">Sending unencrypted emails is like sending post cards â anyone and any system that process your mails can read its content. If you encrypt your emails, you put your message into an envelope that only the recipient of the email can open.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-5">
<h3>What is Enigmail?</h3>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 130%;">Enigmail is a seamlessly integrated security add-on for <a href="https://www.thunderbird.net/" rel="alternate">Mozilla Thunderbird</a>. It allows you to use OpenPGP to encrypt and digitally sign your emails and to decrypt and verify messages you receive.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 130%;">Enigmail is <a href="http://www.gnu.org/philosophy/free-sw.html" rel="alternate">free software</a>. It can be freely used, modified and distributed under the terms of the <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/MPL/2.0/" rel="alternate">Mozilla Public License</a>.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-5">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Start encrypting your emails today!</h3>
<div class="btn-actions">
<p><br/><p style='text-align: center;'><a id='downloadLink' class='btn btn-success btn-lg' href=''>Download Enigmail Now</a></p><p style='text-align: center'><span style='font-size: 8pt;'>Version   -  <a href=''>OpenPGP Signature</a>  -  <a href='/index.php/en/download-old-versions'>Previous Releases</a></span></p></p>
<p>Â </p>
</div>
</div>
</div> 	</section>
  
